### Planetary Boundaries — JRF-Level Concept

Johan Rockström and colleagues (2009) defined **9 Planetary Boundaries** — the safe limits within which humanity can continue to develop without destabilising the Earth system. This is very high-yield for JRF.The key message: 5 of the 9 boundaries have already been crossed. This is the scientific basis for saying humanity's interaction with Earth has become unsustainable.

