Questions on this topic typically come in these forms: "The term Anthropocene was coined by ___" (Paul Crutzen). "The Brundtland Report was published in ___" (1987). "Ecosystem services include which of the following?" "Which planetary boundary has NOT yet been transgressed?" "Environmental Determinism was proposed by ___" (Huntington). "Carrying capacity refers to ___."

For JRF specifically, expect multi-concept questions that link Earth–Man–Environment interaction to climate feedbacks, planetary boundaries, or the history of environmental thought — not just simple definitions.
